    "question": "The project manager of a software development project for a financial institution realizes that team members are unusually delayed on their assigned tasks. The project manager has not experienced this before on previous, similar projects. After further investigation, the project manager determined that the delays were linked to the recent resignation of an experienced team member.\nWhat should the project manager have done to avoid this situation?",
